10. On process to suppress the urge to buy more books and novels (which might not succeed)

12. A forgetful person
13. Indecisive and volatile
14. Emotional eater
15. I like my things tidy and orderly on my own terms.
16. Love-hate relationship in learning mandarin
17. Rather slow in processing and loading things and thoughts

19. Sleeping is a luxury
20. A gemini
